# Task 1 - Bases

1.

```

```

It's a **base32** encoded string. We can use `base32` to decode that:


2. 

```
[Easy] TVJYWEtZVE1NVlBXRVlMVE1WWlE9PT09
```

It seems to me that this is a **`base64`** encoded string. We can use `base64` to decode this:

```
â”Œâ”€â”€(rootðŸŒ¸siunam)-[~/ctf/thm/ctf/Break_it]
â””â”€# echo "TVJYWEtZVE1NVlBXRVlMVE1WWlE9PT09" | base64 -d 
MRXXKYTMMVPWEYLTMVZQ====
```

Double encoded? Another **base32**. We can pipe (`|`) the `base64` decoded output to `base32`:

```
â”Œâ”€â”€(rootðŸŒ¸siunam)-[~/ctf/thm/ctf/Break_it]
â””â”€# echo "TVJYWEtZVE1NVlBXRVlMVE1WWlE9PT09" | base64 -d | base32 -d
double_bases
``` 

3. 

```
[Moderate] GM4HOU3VHBAW6OKNJJFW6SS2IZ3VAMTYORFDMUC2G44EQULIJI3WIVRUMNCWI6KGK5XEKZDTN5YU2RT2MR3E45KKI5TXSOJTKZJTC4KRKFDWKZTZOF3TORJTGZTXGNKCOE======
```

It's a **`base32`** encoded string.

```
â”Œâ”€â”€(rootðŸŒ¸siunam)-[~/ctf/thm/ctf/Break_it]
â””â”€# echo "GM4HOU3VHBAW6OKNJJFW6SS2IZ3VAMTYORFDMUC2G44EQULIJI3WIVRUMNCWI6KGK5XEKZDTN5YU2RT2MR3E45KKI5TXSOJTKZJTC4KRKFDWKZTZOF3TORJTGZTXGNKCOE======" | base32 -d            
38wSu8Ao9MJKoJZFwP2xtJ6PZ78HQhJ7dV4cEdyFWnEdsoqMFzdvNuJGgy93VS1qQQGefyqw7E36gs5Bq
```

We got a **`base58`** string.

```
â”Œâ”€â”€(rootðŸŒ¸siunam)-[~/ctf/thm/ctf/Break_it]
â””â”€# echo "GM4HOU3VHBAW6OKNJJFW6SS2IZ3VAMTYORFDMUC2G44EQULIJI3WIVRUMNCWI6KGK5XEKZDTN5YU2RT2MR3E45KKI5TXSOJTKZJTC4KRKFDWKZTZOF3TORJTGZTXGNKCOE======" | base32 -d | base58 -d
59 6d 46 7a 5a 54 45 32 58 32 6c 7a 58 32 68 6c 65 41 3d 3d    
```

This time we got a **hexadecimal** string. We can use `xxd` to convert to string:

```
â”Œâ”€â”€(rootðŸŒ¸siunam)-[~/ctf/thm/ctf/Break_it]
â””â”€# echo "GM4HOU3VHBAW6OKNJJFW6SS2IZ3VAMTYORFDMUC2G44EQULIJI3WIVRUMNCWI6KGK5XEKZDTN5YU2RT2MR3E45KKI5TXSOJTKZJTC4KRKFDWKZTZOF3TORJTGZTXGNKCOE======" | base32 -d | base58 -d | xxd -r -p
YmFzZTE2X2lzX2hleA==
```

**`base64`** again.

```
â”Œâ”€â”€(rootðŸŒ¸siunam)-[~/ctf/thm/ctf/Break_it]
â””â”€# echo "GM4HOU3VHBAW6OKNJJFW6SS2IZ3VAMTYORFDMUC2G44EQULIJI3WIVRUMNCWI6KGK5XEKZDTN5YU2RT2MR3E45KKI5TXSOJTKZJTC4KRKFDWKZTZOF3TORJTGZTXGNKCOE======" | base32 -d | base58 -d | xxd -r -p | base64 -d   
base16_is_hex
```

Got it!
